{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b489fa71e5","title":"刘涛揭发的王光美与刘少奇的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"b0f71427d1","index":0,"year":1966,"month":7,"day":3,"articleId":"b489fa71e5","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"王光美","id":"1f0a0507bf","type":"人物"},{"name":"刘少奇","id":"3aaab89c2a","type":"人物"},{"name":"资产阶级反动路线","id":"70f02a0dc7","type":"主题"},{"name":"刘涛","id":"8120da8484","type":"人物"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"发言","id":"e23dcf99fa","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"刘少奇","id":"ed8d454915","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"84ad624f40","name":"王光美"},{"id":"9986567b57","name":"刘少奇"},{"id":"ae8a93a2cb","name":"刘涛"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"90e95642d1","type":"title","text":"刘涛揭发的王光美与刘少奇的讲话","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"b489fa71e5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ad35828281","type":"paragraph","text":"（刘涛揭发：）在七月三日晚上我记得她（王光美）跟我讲过一次话……记得有这么几点：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"b489fa71e5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"68cc78bc13","type":"paragraph","text":"一、要把蒯大富当活靶子打。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"b489fa71e5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d6506ba600","type":"paragraph","text":"二、要把蒯大富他们一派搞成少数，批倒了他们才能巩固工作组的地位。三、资产阶级不给我们民主，我们也不给他们民主。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"b489fa71e5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dc5501096e","type":"paragraph","text":"七月二十八日，刘少奇异常激动地对我和王光美说：","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"b489fa71e5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0cced71fa2","type":"paragraph","text":"一、现在不是要检讨吗？要我到你们学校去检讨也可以，去就去，没有什么可怕的。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"b489fa71e5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"41bcd2fca9","type":"paragraph","text":"二、工作组的工作是当着大家的面做的。（意思就是说，是好是坏，大家都能检验出来。）","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"b489fa71e5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7ddaa94831","type":"paragraph","text":"三、工作组现在也没有什么事情了，你们就劳动，帮助抄大字报，扫扫地，这样别的同学也就不会说你们当官做老爷了。四、蒯大富是自己跳出来的，而不是工作组把他打成反革命的。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"b489fa71e5","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}